data.description: Located on US23, just 5 minutes from downtown Big Stone Gap, this three bedroom two bathroom doublewide sits on one acre of land. On one end of the home, you will find the primary bedroom featuring a spacious primary bathroom. The other two bedrooms and guest bathroom are located on the opposite end of the home. Kitchen appliances are included in the sale of the home. Metal roof is only two years old. The heat pump is regularly serviced. Outside you will enjoy beautiful mountain views. There is a outbuilding for extra storage that conveys with the sale. The septic system and entry road is shared. Buyers and buyers agent to verify all information in this listing. All information pulled from public record. Subject to E and O.
